03:48.180 --> 03:50.700
and to bases and fouls.

03:50.700 --> 03:55.660
The bill would give the Congressional committees the final determination of what is not pertinent.

03:55.660 --> 04:00.340
I've been chairman of many investigating committees ranging from the crime committee

04:00.340 --> 04:03.980
into the more complex fields of monopoly legislation.

04:03.980 --> 04:08.580
A good committee doesn't have to violate the bill of rights in order to conduct a thorough

04:08.580 --> 04:10.260
investigation.

04:10.260 --> 04:14.260
And I want the courts to remain as referees over committees.

04:14.260 --> 04:23.340
