05:24.340 --> 05:28.580
We've grown to be a great country by speaking and acting freely.

05:28.580 --> 05:32.740
A quick and easy way to become second-rate is to limit our basic freedoms of thought,

05:32.740 --> 05:35.940
of speech, of press, of religion, and of action.

05:35.940 --> 05:38.940
